  - Ensure the runtime is allowed to use the OpenAI endpoints for functions (the platform must support OpenAI tool routing).

- Using OpenRouter (if your environment expects OpenRouter):
  - Ensure you have an OpenRouter API key.
  - Set environment variable: export OPENROUTER_API_KEY="or-..."
  - Optionally set provider selection, e.g. export OPENROUTER_PROVIDER="openai" or set the provider details in the OpenRouter config following their routing docs.
  - See: https://openrouter.ai/docs/guides/routing/provider-selection for provider selection and routing configuration.

2. If your runtime expects a config file, create or update it per provider docs:
